  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t看新闻发现一个有趣的地方，就是欧美国家的领导人，普遍来说他们的身材都是非常好的，腿细且直，并且很少有大肚子的情况，这点无论是独裁国家还是民主国家的领导人都一样；<br/>\n<br/>\n但是中国就不一样，领导人没一个身材好的，初代的毛，邓不说，后来的胡和习，感觉没一个身材比例好的，要么是五短身材，要么是大腹便便，真是毫无气质……<br/>\n<br/>\n这是怎么回事呢？<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWVmOWNmYjQ0NDM5Y2Q4YTliNGI1LmpwZz93aWR0aD0yMDAwJmhlaWdodD0xMzAx\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1ef9cfb44439cd8a9b4b5.jpg?width=2000&amp;height=1301\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1ef9cfb44439cd8a9b4b5.jpg?width=2000&amp;height=1301\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1ef9cfb44439cd8a9b4b5.jpg?width=2000&amp;height=1301\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYThkOTI5YjYzZmNjNDAwMWNhYjYyLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yNTYwJmhlaWdodD0xNzA3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8d929b63fcc4001cab62.jpg?width=2560&amp;height=1707\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8d929b63fcc4001cab62.jpg?width=2560&amp;height=1707\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a8d929b63fcc4001cab62.jpg?width=2560&amp;height=1707\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTYyOGE1OGY3YTQyZmI0MDZiZWMyLmpwZz93aWR0aD01MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTMwNw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a628a58f7a42fb406bec2.jpg?width=500&amp;height=307\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a628a58f7a42fb406bec2.jpg?width=500&amp;height=307\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a628a58f7a42fb406bec2.jpg?width=500&amp;height=307\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGQ1YjcxOGMxNTNmMDJkNWVjNTdhLmpwZz93aWR0aD04NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTU2MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0d5b718c153f02d5ec